import React from 'react';
import { View, StyleSheet, Text, Image, TextInput, TouchableOpacity, Button } from 'react-native';


export default function Campus({ navigation }) {
    return (
        <View>
            <Text style={styles.tittle}>Selecione o Campus que deseja realizar Checkin</Text>
            <TouchableOpacity
                style={styles.botao}>
                <Text>
                    Campus Zona Sul
            </Text>

            </TouchableOpacity>

            <TouchableOpacity
                style={styles.botao}>
                <Text>
                    Campus FAPA
            </Text>

            </TouchableOpacity>

            <TouchableOpacity
                style={styles.botao}>
                <Text>
                    Campus Canoas
            </Text>

            </TouchableOpacity>

        </View>
    )

}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    container: {
        flex: 1,
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignItems: 'center'
    },
    botao: {
        width: 300,
        height: 70,
        backgroundColor: '#FF4040',
        marginTop: 35,
        alignItems: 'center',
        justifyContent: 'center',
        alignSelf:'center'
    },
    tittle: {
        marginTop: 20,
        fontWeight: "bold",
        fontSize: 15,
        color: "#1C1C1C"
    },

})
